body: They and /r/Retconned colluded once to get me banned from both subs for no reason (because I said CERN wasn't behind it and they're all nuts and must've thought I'm an NPC or something), and 3 times to get me suspended from the whole site (all of which were successful, the last they acted in conjunction with DefaultMods and I got "chucked"). They kept claiming I "ban evaded" for mentioning their subreddits *in other subreddits*. I'm sure the admins knew it was fake but why not take a perfect opportunity to ban me?
